dge, MA.[7] "Product Information. Taltz Autoinjector (ixekizumab)." Eli Lilly and Company, Indianapolis, IN.[8] "Product Information. Cosentyx (secukinumab)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[9] "Product Information. Ilaris (canakinumab)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 'Alteplase, Ascorbic acid, Vitamin A, Potassium Iodide, Acetylcysteine, Nandrolone, Heparin, Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Thalidomide, Belimumab, Emapalumab, Sutimlimab, More', 1767369485);
